Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Over me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'm baptised~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:02.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In your~ ho~ly~ light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And you brought me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In a prison of ice I lived my life in~ pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:26.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just waiting to~ be un~~chained
