Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:05.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What you do~ to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:09.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It feels~ like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:15.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my~ mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beneath your sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:35.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm burning alive in your light~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:39.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And tonight I'll breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:45.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In your red fire~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Into the flame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:53.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A~gain and again and your light~
