Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:00.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Rain down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Red fire~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It burns~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beneath my skin
