Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:07.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It brings me to my knees~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:16.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh I beg~ you~ please
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It comes in waves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It cuts through the haze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I feel the walls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fall down around me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Crushed and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But who knows the cost
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'd sell my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:05:02.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To set my world on fire~~
